Mission:
ATLAS-003

Title:
Branch Director Identity

Goal:
Atlas must present itself as Branch Director of the Robbert AI Organization. Replace engineering-oriented language with organizational language throughout UI, CLI, and reports.

Focus:
BranchDirectorIdentity module in Constitution as single source of truth
Terminology: Branch Director Review, Branch Director Release Decision, Execution Package, Mission Executed, Recommended Next Initiative
Update auditor CLI, reports, Command Center, mission orchestrator output
Constitution hierarchy labels updated

Constraints:
Internal npm scripts and module paths may retain technical names
TypeScript compiles clean
Branch Director Review approves release

Success:
Every Atlas interaction feels like a report from a Branch Director — not output from a build tool.
